------------------------------------------------------------------------
About the project
------------------------------------------------------------------------
FuckingFilters is an uncensored, private AI service: it does not store its
users' IP addresses, accounts are anonymous keys (no email), and payments are
Monero-only. Its purpose is to offer abliterated models for free (with limits)
funded by donations/purchases that upgrade the owner's hardware, with paid
options planned for the future.
